    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i get that but my doctor isn't around and it's a pretty bad headache. i've taken ibuprofen before when my kidneys were better and it never felt like a big deal. like, is it really that dangerous for just one dose of 400mg? it's not like i'm taking it every day.",
