      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of drama for one pill. i'm not in a medical emergency or anything, just a regular headache. are you sure it's actually that immediate of a risk? it feels like you're being super cautious. i just want to know if it's actually going to cause damage right now or if you're just giving me the standard warning.",
